:hasEmail rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
          rdfs:domain :TrainingCentre ;
          rdfs:range xsd:string ;
          rdfs:comment "Email of a training centre"@en ;
          rdfs:label "has email"@en .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/eNOVATION-ontology#hasEvaluationComments
